\u6027\u4e4b\u57ce\u300b</li>\n<li>\u300a\u5973\u6743\u8fa9\u62a4\u300b</li>\n<li>\u300a\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u4e00\u95f4\u5c4b\u300b(a room of one's own)</li>\n<li>\u300a\u7b2c\u4e8c\u6027...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-11-07T00:00:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["feminism"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "title": "About", "content_html": "<h1>My online wiki</h1>\n<p>The math note part, I'm using zotero, obsidian and mkdocs to create this wiki, and is hosted on github pages.</p>\n<p>&lt;!-- - [About](/wiki/About/in...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "title": "This is my Notes about computer", "content_html": "<h1>This is my Notes about computer</h1>\n<p>Concludes linux, software, latex, etc</p>\n<h2>linux and code</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/code/archinstall\">install arch</a></li>\n<li>[git note](wiki/code/g...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/btrfs/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/btrfs/", "title": "\u7528btrfs\u505alinux\u7684\u5feb\u7167\u5907\u4efd", "content_html": "<h1>btrfs \u7684\u5907\u4efd</h1>\n<h2>timeshift and snapper</h2>\n<h2>timeshift \u5907\u4efd\u6839\u76ee\u5f55</h2>\n<h2>snapper \u5907\u4efd\u5b50\u5377</h2>\n<p>snapper\u66f4\u52a0\u7075\u6d3b</p>\n<p>\u9009\u62e9\u4f7f\u7528\n```\nbtrfs subvolume create /mnt/@snapshots # \u5982\u679c\u4f7f\u7528 snapper \u4f5c\u4e3a\u56de\u6eda\u5de5\u5177\uff0c...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["arch"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/examples/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/examples/", "title": "examples", "content_html": "<h1>examples</h1>\n<h2>Text Formatting</h2>\n<p><code>md\n- [ ] ==Get==\n- [-] things\n- [x] ~~done~~</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>[ ] ==Get==</li>\n<li>[-] things</li>\n<li>[x] ~~done~~</li>\n</ul>\n<p>More formatting options for y...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/arch/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/arch/", "title": "Index", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/", "title": "Index", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/life/", "title": "Life Hacker!", "content_html": "<h1>Life Hacker!</h1>\n<p>\u8fd9\u91cc\u662f\u4e00\u4e9b\u5173\u4e8e\u201c\u5982\u4f55\u751f\u6d3b\u201d\u7684\u7b14\u8bb0\u3002\u6d3b\u7740\u592atm\u7d2f\u4e86\uff0c\u627e\u5230\u6539\u5584\u6e38\u620f\u96be\u5ea6\u7684\u4f5c\u5f0a\u7801\uff0c\u6216\u8005\u53d1\u73b0\u8212\u9002\u5708\u5c0f\u6e38\u620f\uff0c\u5f53\u7136\u5e94\u8be5\u8bb0\u4e0b\u6765\u5566\u3002</p>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/life/cocktail\">\u559d\u9152\uff01</a></p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/", "title": "My math Notes", "content_html": "<h1>My math Notes</h1>\n<p>Mainly Algebraic Geometry</p>\n<h2>Basic AG</h2>\n<p>Hartshorne, EGA, etc</p>\n<h2>Birational Geomatry</h2>\n<h3>Pre BCHM</h3>\n<p>KM98</p>\n<h3>BCHM</h3>\n<p>bchm</p>\n<h3>Post BCHM</h3>\n<p>bir12.\nNon-Q-...</p>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/math/BCHM/", "title": "BCHM", "content_html": "<h1>BCHM</h1>\n<h2>PreBCHM</h2>\n<p>including KM98<br>\n we can run mmp for klt Q-factorial pairs, except existence of flip.</p>\n<h2>BCHM</h2>\n<p>MMP for $(X,B)$ klt and $B$ big</p>\n<h2>PostBCH...</h2>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}]}